  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"SD Dungeons\" is a top-down rogue-like action game.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your character to your liking with a variety of parts and accessories,<br>then choose your favorite from six different jobs.<br>Utilize unique skills and actions for each job and weapon to reach the depths of the dungeon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through randomly generated dungeon floors,<br>you’ll encounter monsters, traps, and fate-changing gates.<br>Beyond the gate awaits paradise, hell… or perhaps a formidable boss!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You might obtain powerful weapons and armor from treasure chests, monsters, or bosses!<br>Will you push forward in search of legendary items,<br>or escape safely to steadily accumulate gear and experience? The choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＜Character Creation＞</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from various hairstyles, hair colors, eyes, and accessories to create your perfect look!<br>Whether cute or cool, design your character just the way you like!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/c17563377e58c935a210d571a56b79e8.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=398 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/c17563377e58c935a210d571a56b79e8.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/c17563377e58c935a210d571a56b79e8.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/6165c69b1aeb2383b39d85aacb68a54c.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=656 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/6165c69b1aeb2383b39d85aacb68a54c.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/6165c69b1aeb2383b39d85aacb68a54c.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＜Dungeon＞</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features two types of challenges:<br>randomly generated <strong>\"Dungeons\"</strong> and fixed-stage <strong>\"Quests.\"</strong><br>Want to test out different jobs or weapons? Try the Quest mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/556bf057addd2e693d7747b8abffd641.avif?t=1743735622\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras_big/556bf057addd2e693d7747b8abffd641.avif?t=1743735622 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/77eb6d851f650e8269b5b7f9e5fbf752.avif?t=1743735622\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras_big/77eb6d851f650e8269b5b7f9e5fbf752.avif?t=1743735622 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＜Gates＞</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many types of gates, such as the <strong>\"Normal Gate,\"</strong> <strong>\"Gate of Ruin,\"</strong> and <strong>\"Escape Gate.\"</strong><br>A variety of gates appear randomly at each floor transition,<br>and the one you choose will determine the difficulty of the next floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/433eb68f3dffb0e026c229c2e315f42d.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=538 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/433eb68f3dffb0e026c229c2e315f42d.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/433eb68f3dffb0e026c229c2e315f42d.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＜Jobs＞</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from six unique jobs!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Fighter</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A melee job that wields a sword and shield.<br>With balanced attack and defense, it’s easy to handle.<br>Switch between standard attacks and counters to control the fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/9c4133186c0adc984c3b4a432a0e3acf.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/9c4133186c0adc984c3b4a432a0e3acf.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/9c4133186c0adc984c3b4a432a0e3acf.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Ranger</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long-range job that uses a bow.<br>Low defense, but exceptional range!<br>Take advantage of distance to attack freely!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/3467888d8cecf1753206395c1751708f.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=414 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/3467888d8cecf1753206395c1751708f.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/3467888d8cecf1753206395c1751708f.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Sorcerer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long-range job that wields a staff.<br>Like the Ranger, it has low defense, but can cast powerful magic.<br>Charge your magic to alter its effects!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/518726bbd38d98fe6586ad3e96db19e2.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=390 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/518726bbd38d98fe6586ad3e96db19e2.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/518726bbd38d98fe6586ad3e96db19e2.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Monk</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A melee job that fights with fists and dual daggers.<br>Lower attack and defense, with short range, but excellent mobility.<br>Dodge enemy attacks and strike relentlessly as an infighter!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/33906bf91b1a77f976780e1494e252ab.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=404 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/33906bf91b1a77f976780e1494e252ab.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/33906bf91b1a77f976780e1494e252ab.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Warrior</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A melee job that wields a greatsword.<br>Slow movement, but devastating attack power.<br>Observe enemy movements and land a mighty blow!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/afbe3397730eb3b309cd717a0beb214a.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=350 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/afbe3397730eb3b309cd717a0beb214a.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/afbe3397730eb3b309cd717a0beb214a.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Gunner</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A ranged job that uses dual guns.<br>Shorter range than the Ranger, but allows for rapid attacks.<br>Take down enemies with stylish shooting action!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/9b070f6ea207edec2344fc1c4356c570.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=380 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/9b070f6ea207edec2344fc1c4356c570.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/9b070f6ea207edec2344fc1c4356c570.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"SD Dungeons\" is a top-down rogue-like action game.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your character to your liking with a variety of parts and accessories,<br>then choose your favorite from six different jobs.<br>Utilize unique skills and actions for each job and weapon to reach the depths of the dungeon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through randomly generated dungeon floors,<br>you’ll encounter monsters, traps, and fate-changing gates.<br>Beyond the gate awaits paradise, hell… or perhaps a formidable boss!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You might obtain powerful weapons and armor from treasure chests, monsters, or bosses!<br>Will you push forward in search of legendary items,<br>or escape safely to steadily accumulate gear and experience? The choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＜Character Creation＞</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from various hairstyles, hair colors, eyes, and accessories to create your perfect look!<br>Whether cute or cool, design your character just the way you like!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/c17563377e58c935a210d571a56b79e8.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=398 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/c17563377e58c935a210d571a56b79e8.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/c17563377e58c935a210d571a56b79e8.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/6165c69b1aeb2383b39d85aacb68a54c.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=656 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/6165c69b1aeb2383b39d85aacb68a54c.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/6165c69b1aeb2383b39d85aacb68a54c.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＜Dungeon＞</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features two types of challenges:<br>randomly generated <strong>\"Dungeons\"</strong> and fixed-stage <strong>\"Quests.\"</strong><br>Want to test out different jobs or weapons? Try the Quest mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/556bf057addd2e693d7747b8abffd641.avif?t=1743735622\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras_big/556bf057addd2e693d7747b8abffd641.avif?t=1743735622 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/77eb6d851f650e8269b5b7f9e5fbf752.avif?t=1743735622\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras_big/77eb6d851f650e8269b5b7f9e5fbf752.avif?t=1743735622 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＜Gates＞</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many types of gates, such as the <strong>\"Normal Gate,\"</strong> <strong>\"Gate of Ruin,\"</strong> and <strong>\"Escape Gate.\"</strong><br>A variety of gates appear randomly at each floor transition,<br>and the one you choose will determine the difficulty of the next floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/433eb68f3dffb0e026c229c2e315f42d.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=538 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/433eb68f3dffb0e026c229c2e315f42d.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/433eb68f3dffb0e026c229c2e315f42d.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＜Jobs＞</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from six unique jobs!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Fighter</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A melee job that wields a sword and shield.<br>With balanced attack and defense, it’s easy to handle.<br>Switch between standard attacks and counters to control the fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/9c4133186c0adc984c3b4a432a0e3acf.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/9c4133186c0adc984c3b4a432a0e3acf.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/9c4133186c0adc984c3b4a432a0e3acf.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Ranger</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long-range job that uses a bow.<br>Low defense, but exceptional range!<br>Take advantage of distance to attack freely!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/3467888d8cecf1753206395c1751708f.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=414 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/3467888d8cecf1753206395c1751708f.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/3467888d8cecf1753206395c1751708f.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Sorcerer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long-range job that wields a staff.<br>Like the Ranger, it has low defense, but can cast powerful magic.<br>Charge your magic to alter its effects!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/518726bbd38d98fe6586ad3e96db19e2.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=390 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/518726bbd38d98fe6586ad3e96db19e2.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/518726bbd38d98fe6586ad3e96db19e2.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Monk</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A melee job that fights with fists and dual daggers.<br>Lower attack and defense, with short range, but excellent mobility.<br>Dodge enemy attacks and strike relentlessly as an infighter!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/33906bf91b1a77f976780e1494e252ab.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=404 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/33906bf91b1a77f976780e1494e252ab.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/33906bf91b1a77f976780e1494e252ab.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Warrior</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A melee job that wields a greatsword.<br>Slow movement, but devastating attack power.<br>Observe enemy movements and land a mighty blow!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/afbe3397730eb3b309cd717a0beb214a.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=350 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/afbe3397730eb3b309cd717a0beb214a.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/afbe3397730eb3b309cd717a0beb214a.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■ Gunner</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A ranged job that uses dual guns.<br>Shorter range than the Ranger, but allows for rapid attacks.<br>Take down enemies with stylish shooting action!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/9b070f6ea207edec2344fc1c4356c570.poster.avif?t=1743735622\" width=380 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/9b070f6ea207edec2344fc1c4356c570.webm?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621980/extras/9b070f6ea207edec2344fc1c4356c570.mp4?t=1743735622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
